---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Community Garden" description="The New Era Community Garden at 26th & B — 41 plots, a Friend of the Garden program, and potlucks. Reborn in 2024.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <p class="accent-script">Reborn & blooming</p>
      <h1>New Era Community Garden</h1>
      <p>
        Our community garden has been reborn! After two years sitting vacant,
        MNENA secured a 5-year lease on the property and restarted the garden
        at 26th &amp; B Streets in fall 2024. All 41 plots were snapped up
        quickly, but we keep a waiting list for anyone interested.
      </p>

      <h2>Friend of the Garden 🌻</h2>
      <p>
        No plot? No problem. Friends of the Garden enjoy time in the garden
        without managing a plot (great while you're on the waitlist too).
        Annual FOG membership is <strong>$20</strong> and includes access to
        the garden plus invitations to every garden event — including the
        potlucks.
      </p>

      <h2>2025 highlights</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Cleared out all the weeds and overgrown brush for spring planting</li>
        <li>Built a beautiful new garden shed</li>
        <li>Won a City of Sacramento Integrated Pest Management grant, funding native and drought-tolerant plants to attract pollinators</li>
        <li>Hosted a spring block party at the garden — enjoyed by hundreds of neighbors</li>
        <li>Organized potluck dinners and brunches so gardeners could connect without getting their hands dirty</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="card" style="margin-top: var(--space-xl);">
        <h3>Get involved</h3>
        <p>
          Want plot waitlist info, or to become a Friend of the Garden? Email
          <a href="mailto:garden@marshallnewera.org">garden@marshallnewera.org</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
